{"tid":2297663,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"親愛的老公：餘生，請多多指教","createTime":"2020-11-23T12:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T22:33:11.000Z","uid":101341,"like":67,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c55f0ba1f829b9796e30ee726987e56e79d910cb","tid":2297663,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"親愛的老公：<br />\n<br />\n現在是清晨七點鐘，你每天起床的時間。但今天是周末，所以此刻的你正輕輕地打着呼嚕，睡意正酣。<br />\n<br />\n我不忍破壞這份寧靜，但又情不自禁地甜蜜：上天真的過於優愛我，派了你來守候我。<br />\n<br />\n我曾經以為，這輩子都不會結婚了。<br />\n<br />\n世界這麼大，我又不夠優秀，不能閃光到讓別人注意到我的存在，萬一你找不到我怎麼辦。<br />\n<br />\n但還好，雖然等的時間久了些，最終你還是出現了。<br />\n<br />\n有人說：夫妻本事同林鳥，大難臨頭各自飛。<br />\n<br />\n他們把神聖的婚姻簡單的理解成了搭夥過日子，抱團取暖。對婚姻缺乏了一種敬畏心，似乎只要去政府提交了申請就能結婚。<br />\n<br />\n但他們忘記了，領了結婚證不代表就是戀人夫妻。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的戀人夫妻，就是即使沒有血緣關係，也願意風風雨雨，同舟共濟。<br />\n所謂的戀人夫妻，就是經得起生活的平淡，承擔得起歲月的變遷。<br />\n所謂的戀人夫妻，就是今世和你牽手，來世還想一起走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千年修得同船渡，百年修得共枕眠。每一對至親至愛夫妻，都是上輩子千年的回眸，才換回今世相守。<br />\n<br />\n而你我，就是這樣的夫妻。<br />\n<br />\n只要能和你在一起，再簡單的生活都是最幸福的事。<br />\n<br />\n我當過別人的女兒，別人的朋友，唯獨沒當過別人的老婆。初為人妻，如有不周，還請多多指教。"},{"pid":"41d7b360331b69009949220a9a23b3d2ca0146f7","tid":2297663,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f9a4b6c88de60032c505b7bcaffa1dda602d43","tid":2297663,"uid":256362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"你贏，好浪漫。"},{"pid":"40f1c628514aba5b10f54d5065bc55f71820f332","tid":2297663,"uid":40397,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"衰婆，邊個係余生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34599f28e08265397769dd0349feba7cf1d63192","tid":2297663,"uid":54927,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"98f9a4b6c88de60032c505b7bcaffa1dda602d43","tid":2297663,"uid":256362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"你贏，好浪漫。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"大陸嗰啲雞湯文<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19dfdd010e60049e7bf9bb3cae0e84914b03ec36","tid":2297663,"uid":368719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"放心，我會好好照顏你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783651a7e947144bb898f3028bdde3c119505a84","tid":2297663,"uid":108756,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"別說那麼多 來 用口來"},{"pid":"61f7fe430fedf0582c779d62e6614e5cb77014f5","tid":2297663,"uid":186708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:37:09.000Z","msg":"老婆，麼麼噠"},{"pid":"a3320a1f01c46501b981d2c3e4d260e9a31fa7d5","tid":2297663,"uid":145755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:39:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 冇人會同你結婚"},{"pid":"fd2dff8c906174c14a2b091f4dfff82786a61eae","tid":2297663,"uid":147351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f1c628514aba5b10f54d5065bc55f71820f332","tid":2297663,"uid":40397,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"衰婆，邊個係余生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca5f771bbee3c4f2d2151edacd5f41c75046478","tid":2297663,"uid":115715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"岩岩俾老婆飛左 一路睇一路笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753dfe2b52949d653b52c1e0efbaf70439ecea07","tid":2297663,"uid":68661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T22:33:11.000Z","msg":"當連登係fb？"}]}